RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTB_CONTRACT A, OLTMS_CONTRACT_USERDEF_FIELDS B WHERE A.MODULE_CODE IN ('OL', 'LB') AND A.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'L' AND A.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND B.VERSION_NO = (SELECT MAX(VERSION_NO) FROM OLTMS_CONTRACT_USERDEF_FIELDS WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND B.FIELD_NAME = 'LERETAREFNO' AND B.FIELD_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND A.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH ORDER BY A.CONTRACT_REF_NO

SELECT ALL OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_NAME COUNTY_CODE, OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_DESC COUNTY_NAME FROM OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS WHERE OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_TYPE = 'CNTY' AND OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_NAME

SELECT ALL OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_NAME STATE_CODE, OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_DESC STATE_NAME FROM OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS WHERE OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_TYPE = 'STAT' AND OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_NAME

SELECT ALL OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_NAME PRIMARY_DESC_CODE, OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_DESC PRIMARY_DESC FROM OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS WHERE OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_TYPE = 'DESC' AND OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS.FIELD_NAME
